---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | The Birdie Report"
  description="How The Birdie Report earns revenue through affiliate partnerships."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-6">
      <p>
        The Birdie Report is reader-supported. When you buy through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission at no additional cost to you. This helps us keep the lights on and continue producing honest, in-depth golf content.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">How It Works</h2>
      <p>
        We partner with retailers like Amazon, GlobalGolf, and major golf brands through their affiliate programs. When you click a product link on our site and make a purchase, we receive a small percentage of the sale. The price you pay remains the same whether you use our link or go directly to the retailer.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Our Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate partnerships never influence our reviews or recommendations. We recommend products based on real-world testing and honest evaluation. If something sucks, we'll tell you — even if we'd make money recommending it. Our reputation matters more than any commission.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Amazon Associates Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        The Birdie Report is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships, feel free to <a href="/contact/" class="text-green-700 hover:text-green-800 underline">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
